{{Infobox waterfall | name = Hurkalo | photo = Gurkalo.JPG | photo_width = | photo_caption = | map = | map_width = | region = | source = | coords_ref = | location = [[Skole Raion]], [[Lviv Oblast]], [[Ukraine]] | type = | elevation = | height = {{convert|5|m|ft}} | height_longest = | number_drops = 1 | width = {{convert|4|m|ft}} | average_width = | watercourse = Velyka Richka River | average_flow = | world_rank = }}
The '''Hurkalo''' ({{lang-uk|Гуркало}}) waterfall is located on the Velyka Richka River, {{convert|3|km}} south-west of Korchyn, [[Skole Raion]], [[Lviv Oblast]] of western [[Ukraine]]. The waterfall is {{convert|5|m|ft}} high.
