The '''Kumano Sea''' is a body of water belonging to [[North Pacific Ocean]] ([[Philippines Sea]]) located off the coast of [[Kumano Region]] of the [[Kii Peninsula]] located in central [[Japan]].<ref>[http://www.geographic.org/geographic_names/name.php?uni=-352190&fid=3223&c=japan Geographical Names]</ref>

